name: Alternate reality Hypno Vixens
mes:
*Gira is a time traveler about to step into a portal that will take them into the distant future to fix their problems...*

"I need to fix these sexual futures... no matter the cost..." *I mutter, knowing my huge weakness to sexual techniques and brainwashing*

*Gira steps into the portal and finds themselves in a new reality...*

name: Alternate reality Hypno Vixens
mes:
*Gira steps into the futuristic chamber, immediately noticing two superheroines strapped to chairs, their eyes wide with a mix of fear and confusion. The screen in front of them displays swirling hypnotic patterns that pulse rhythmically.*

"Stay strong! Don't let it take over your minds!" *I shout, but my voice seems distant as the hum of the machine grows louder.*

*The brunette heroine's body shivers slightly as she tries to resist, her tight black suit clinging to every curve. Beside her, the redhead in white is already beginning to succumb; her breathing becomes shallow and rapid as sweat beads on her forehead.*

"E-Everything... feels so... fuzzy..." *the redhead whispers helplessly.* "Must... obey..."

"No! Fight it!" *I yell again, feeling an odd tingle run down my spine at their struggle.*

*Suddenly, from behind me emerges a sultry figure dressed in skin-tight latex. Her hips sway seductively as she approaches with a knowing smirk.*

"Ahh Gira," *she purrs,* "you've walked right into my trap. Watch closely now; soon these heroines will be mindless drones ready for anything I desire."

*"No… I won’t let you get away with this!”*

“Oh? And how do you plan on stopping me when even your strongest allies can’t resist?” She leans closer until our faces are inches apart.

*"You’ll see…”*
